item.title: How to fix this? (using Deathlypvpz source)
item.dc:creator: @arham_4 arham 4
item.description:
@arham_4 wrote:

There is something already using port 43594/5555. Try to switch the ports around.

So if the port is 43594, make it 5555.
If the port is 5555, make it 43594.
